From: Patch Piper <patchpiper@clickup>
Subject: [PATCH] fix: resolve 3 Dart compile errors causing APK build failure

Bug 1 (results_screen.dart): Type 'Mistake' not found.
  Fix: rename field type to MistakeItem (the real model class in game_config.dart).

Bug 2 (profile_screen.dart): List<dynamic> cannot be assigned to
  List<Map<String,dynamic>>. Fix: add .cast<Map<String,dynamic>>().

Bug 3 (meaning_chase_builder.dart): Single-quoted string with phrase['en']
  closes the outer string at the apostrophe before 'en'. Fix: use
  double-quoted key phrase["en"] inside string interpolation.

Apply with:
  git apply --ignore-whitespace fix-build-errors.patch
  git commit -m "fix: resolve 3 Dart compile errors causing release APK failure"
  git push
  rm fix-build-errors.patch
---
 lib/features/games/logic/builders/meaning_chase_builder.dart | 2 +-
 lib/features/profile/screens/profile_screen.dart             | 2 +-
 lib/features/results/screens/results_screen.dart             | 2 +-
 3 files changed, 3 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/lib/features/games/logic/builders/meaning_chase_builder.dart b/lib/features/games/logic/builders/meaning_chase_builder.dart
index ee55aa7..0000000 100644
--- a/lib/features/games/logic/builders/meaning_chase_builder.dart
+++ b/lib/features/games/logic/builders/meaning_chase_builder.dart
@@ -158,7 +158,7 @@ class MeaningChaseBuilder extends McqQuestionBuilder {
           correctAnswer: correct,
-          questionText: '"${phrase['en']}" বাক্যাংশটির বাংলা অর্থ কী?',
+          questionText: '"${phrase["en"]}" বাক্যাংশটির বাংলা অর্থ কী?',
           wordId: phrase['id'] as int,
         ));
 
